resolution_steps: Maribella confirmed Jeff's identity and origin.
Maribella checked Vicki's availability and informed Jeff she was unavailable.
Maribella offered to take a message and confirm a callback number.
Jeff provided his phone number (336-377-9003) and confirmed willingness to leave another message.
Maribella agreed to relay the message and ensure Vicki contacts Jeff.
knowledge_required: Call handling procedures for unavailable contacts
summary: Jeff Edmonds from Alliance Insurance attempted to reach Vicki but was informed she was unavailable. The agent, Maribella, took a message and confirmed a callback number. Jeff provided his contact details and mentioned a prior message, leading to a promise of follow-up by Vicki.
